OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,FAaron Wainwright has become the third
OL,7,Fprominent Welsh international in
OL,8,Frecent weeks to announce a move away
OL,9,Ffrom Welsh rugby as Leicester Tigers
OL,10,Fconfirm the signing of the backrower.
OL,12,FWainwright, who has 62 caps for Wales,
OL,13,Fhas spent the entirety of his
OL,14,Fprofessional career so far at the
OL,15,FDragons. However it has now been
OL,16,Fannounced he will be moving to the
OL,17,FGallagher Prem next season.
