OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,FHe follows Welsh captains Jac Morgan
OL,7,Fand Dewi Lake across the border to
OL,8,FEngland after it was announced the
OL,9,FOspreys duo would be joining
OL,10,FGloucester.
OL,12,FThe departures come at an uncertain
OL,13,Ftime for the game, with the number of
OL,14,Fprofessional clubs set to be reduced
OL,15,Ffrom four to three by 2027 under Welsh
OL,16,FRugby Union plans.
