OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,FThe Dragons confirmed the news and
OL,7,Fsaid the club "tried everything to
OL,8,Fretain his services" including
OL,9,F"financial terms that surpassed all
OL,10,Fothers".
OL,12,FIn a statement they said: "Aaron has
OL,13,Fbeen a fantastic servant for Dragons
OL,14,FRFC, making 129 appearances since his
OL,15,Fdebut in October 2017. His outstanding
OL,16,Fform for the Men of Gwent has rightly
OL,17,Fseen him recognised by Wales, with 62
OL,18,Finternational caps.
