OL,6,F"He is a homegrown success story who
OL,7,Fcame through the Dragons Academy to
OL,8,Fbecome a leading figure in our senior
OL,9,Fside.
OL,11,F"We are obviously disappointed to be
OL,12,Flosing a player of the quality of
OL,13,FAaron at the end of this campaign, and
OL,14,Fwe tried everything to retain his
OL,15,Fservices with financial terms that
OL,16,Fsurpassed all others to remain with us.
