OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,F"However, we must respect his decision
OL,7,Fto want to experience a fresh
OL,8,Fchallenge outside of Wales and know
OL,9,Fhow hard this choice has been for him
OL,10,Fto make. Dragons RFC is his club.
OL,11,FRodney Parade will always be his home.
OL,13,F"Aaron's focus is fully on the
OL,14,Fremainder of this season and helping
OL,15,Four club build on recent performances
OL,16,Fand the New Year's Day derby victory
OL,17,Fover Scarlets that started 2026 on
OL,18,Fsuch a strong footing.
