OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,F"We know Aaron will continue give
OL,7,Feverything to our cause ` as he always
OL,8,Fhas - and be a fantastic role model to
OL,9,Fthe younger players around him in our
OL,10,Fsquad."
OL,12,FHe will join international teammates
OL,13,FOlly Cracknell and Tommy Reffell in
OL,14,FLeicester.
OL,16,FIn a statement, Aaron said: "Dragons
OL,17,FRFC and the Gwent region means a huge
OL,18,Famount to me but now is the right time
OL,19,Fin my career for a fresh challenge. I
OL,20,Fhope all supporters can understand and
OL,21,Fsupport the decision I've made.
