OL,3,CThird international player announces
OL,4,Cmove away from Welsh rugby
OL,6,F"The time to reflect will come at the
OL,7,Fend of this season. Right now, my
OL,8,Ffocus will remain on looking forward
OL,9,Fand building on our recent
OL,10,Fperformances.
OL,12,F"Thank you for your continued support.
OL,13,FThe atmosphere on New Year's Day sums
OL,14,Fup why this is such a special club to
OL,15,Frepresent and be a part of.
OL,17,F"Playing at Rodney Parade will always
OL,18,Fmean the world to me - I look forward
OL,19,Fto more games with the terrace in full
OL,20,Fvoice and the fans behind us before
OL,21,Fthe season is out."
